author: @vish183
text: Hey Krish, great content. However, i have a grave concern to share. Why do all Data Science youtubers consider a dataset which has no null or categorical values whilst they touch upon such crucial topics? Main challenge is in understanding how to use various topics when we have heterogenous data.   I guess, you might have good reasons to consider absolutely clean data, but i feel it defeats the purpose when the situation in real world is lot different from whats shown in tutorials.
